ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisReappointment of CLAIRE ANDERSON of Whitehorse, Yukon, as a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years and her designation for the British Columbia/Yukon region, effective August 26, 2024.
